oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: VINNY Invitation 25 Rockin at the Ryman
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Ryman Auditorium (Nashville, Tenn.); Woodcuts (prints); fund raising; Musical instruments; Guitar; Gill, Vince;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (gray and red on white) announcing the VINNY Invitational 25 with Vince Gill at the Ryman on May 22. Poster features woodcuts of a golf ball and guitars. The event is a charity golf tournament hosted by the country music entertainer Vince Gill to benefit junior golf and youth development programs in Tennessee.
